  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this clinical trial study,the investigators intend to compare two methods of trichiasis
      treatment.One by argon laser and the other by radiofrequency then compare the result of these
      procedures, especially, the investigators would like to compare which of these have less
      complications such as bleeding,pain,notch in the site of surgery and etc.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
